asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

name: Serenity
description: The Fluffle murmurs in a deep slumber. Serenity is awake. Meditating. Searching his soul and preparing for what comes next. He is ever mindful of the commitment he made to Thumper and Scrooge. They have complete faith in him. Tick tock. Tick tock. Tick tock. Mindfulness and peace. Responsible for the spiritual wellbeing of the Fluffle, Serenity was chosen to put others first and himself last. It was not always like this, though. As a child and young adult, Serenity was a problem. Straight up. He was defiant. A troublemaker. A self centered, grumpy Fluf. Folks stayed clear of Serenity and he ran his life into the ground. Literally. But something happened one day. A moment of grace, as they call it, and Serenity was forever changed. He tapped into a higher power and began his spiritual journey, digging into the burrow deeper than any previous Fluf ever had. He certainly never wished to be Fluf Worlds Spiritual Adviser but his higher power had other plans for him.  And here we are. The awakening is happening. Serenity has developed a quiet confidence and Flufs are beginning to seek him for answers. He was born for this moment and will help Fluf World maintain the balance it deserves. Tick tock. Tick tock. Tick tock.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.
